channel.title: Read i need help
channel.description: I was setting up my server and i got to the part where you run the client and source... but When i click run it wont open... it comes up then closes right away.. any ideas?

item.title: Read i need help
item.dc:creator: @Mario_PvP Mario PvP
item.description:
@Mario_PvP wrote:

have you enter the correct JDK version? (in the batch file)
example
@echo off
title RuneScape
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk[size=14pt]1.6.0_02[/size]\bin\java.exe”
pause

Replace [size=14pt]1.6.0_02[/size] with [size=14pt]your[/size] version of JDK
